      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom condition. This masterpiece has been preserved to an exacting standard, exhibiting a flawless aesthetic and a mechanical profile that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled environment, this investment-grade example represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers an unrivaled ownership experience.",
