    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of automotive elegance. This isn't just a car; it's a curated experience of sun-drenched coastal drives and moonlit escapes. Every curve of its hand-polished silhouette captures the light like a fine jewel, while the interior welcomes you with the intoxicating scent of untouched leather and the cold touch of precision-milled aluminum. This vehicle possesses a soul that hums in perfect harmony with the road, offering a driving purity that modern machines have long forgotten. To own this is to possess a masterpiece that looks as though it was driven straight out of a designer\u2019s fever dream and into your garage. It is, quite simply, perfection preserved.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. This specimen has been maintained to the highest standards, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous care. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers unparalleled quality and lasting value.",
